Motormaster continues to stare down Optimal Prime. His eyes narrow 
with rage, but he did'nt even flinch at the warning fire. "Well 
Prime, if you dont want to become a ghost, I suggest you leave now" 
he threatened, then pointed to Cyclonus, Scourge, Drag Strip, Dead-
End, Wildrider, Nightstrike, Switchblade and Megatron. "We slightly 
outnumber you" he growled.
